videos.headline: Coach makes heartfelt dedication to colleague
videos.description: Little Rock women's basketball coach Joe Foley receives the 2016-2017 Sun Belt coach of the year award and promptly gives the trophy to Appalachian State University coach Angel Elderkin, who has been battling cancer.
